  "title": "Core Concepts of Cooking Chicken Curry",
  "lessonText": "Understanding the basics of chicken curry is essential for creating a delicious dish.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Chicken curry is a flavorful dish made with chicken, spices, and sauce.\n- Key ingredients include chicken, onions, tomatoes, and various spices.\n- Cooking techniques vary but often include sautéing, simmering, and blending.\n- The balance of spices is crucial for authentic flavor.\n- Serve with rice or bread for a complete meal."
  }
